#Oriol Barbany 

is a first year PhD student at the Institut de Robòtica i Informàtica Industrial (IRI) and he will visit the École Polytechnique Fédérale de Lausanne (EPFL) in his second PhD year as part of the ELLIS PhD & PostDoc program.

Previously, he worked on the learning-to-rank problem during an internship at Amazon and on voice conversion at Logitech. He hold a Master's degree in Data Science from EPFL and a Bachelor's Degree in Telecommunications Technologies and Services Engineering from UPC.
